{"article_id":"9tYzT5jyvssNgHK0","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"While congressional Republicans have seized on the Supreme Court ' s ruling","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that President Obama ' s health care overhaul is constitutional as a tax ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"presumptive GOP presidential nominee Mitt Romney ' s top campaign strategist undercut that line of argument Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that the governor agrees with Mr. Obama","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that the law is not a tax .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"\" The governor has consistently described the mandate in Massachusetts as a penalty , \"","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Eric Fehrnstrom , Mr. Romney ' s strategist , said on MSNBC .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" The governor disagreed with the ruling of the court ;","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he agreed with the dissent","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that was written by Justice Scalia ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"which clearly states","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the mandate was not a tax . \"","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"During the congressional debate Mr. Obama and his allies repeatedly said","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"the punishment","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"levied against those","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"who fail to obtain health insurance","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"was a penalty , not a tax .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"During the court battle , however , his legal team switched","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"it was , in fact , a tax","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"- and a majority of the court agreed ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that made it constitutional .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"But after the ruling Mr. Obama switched back ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"it isn ' t a tax after all .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Republicans on Capitol Hill and in the states gleefully seized on the majority ' s opinion ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"it will bolster their arguments for repeal","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"as they face voters this November .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"it constitutes a tax","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"because that ' s what the Supreme Court says , \"","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Utah Gov . Gary R. Herbert said on MSNBC shortly after Mr. Fehrnstrom ' s remarks .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"\" I ' ve always believed","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"it was unconstitutional","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"because it was sold to us as a Commerce Clause mandate . \"","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Instead of the tax argument , Mr. Fehrstrom said","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"they will demand","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Obama be held accountable for the conflicting statements","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"on whether the mandate is a penalty or a tax .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Mr. Fehrnstrom also said","depth":2},{"id":43,"text":"that the campaign has raised $ 6.7 million online","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"and attracted more than 70,000 donations in the days","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"following Thursday ' s ruling .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":91,"left":87,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":72,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":58,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":51,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":51,"left":47,"right":50,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":47,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":50,"left":2,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":49,"left":3,"right":48,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":48,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":57,"left":52,"right":56,"relation":"